    "description": "Path of the Oxiflame is a 3D sokoban-puzzle-adventure inspired by classic Team Ico games.<br>This demo features the first two areas of the game.<br><br>A boy finds himself in rough shape in an unfamiliar forest. Strange monuments line the path etched with peculiar markings. On a clearing he discovers a brasier, which burns bright with a green flame. It is said that it holds great power...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174450/extras/5a5303ad6c9f04c232de943d2364a20c.poster.avif?t=1726865706\" width=600 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174450/extras/5a5303ad6c9f04c232de943d2364a20c.webm?t=1726865706\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174450/extras/5a5303ad6c9f04c232de943d2364a20c.mp4?t=1726865706\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Aided by the flame, the boy is able to move the massive boulders which can be found all throughout the confines of the forest.<br>Whoever placed them did it with purpose as if to test someone. But once moved into the correct configuration they reveal the path forward.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174450/extras/e7c5ef57f3256e635c6e6e794ac0d5d9.poster.avif?t=1726865706\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174450/extras/e7c5ef57f3256e635c6e6e794ac0d5d9.webm?t=1726865706\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174450/extras/e7c5ef57f3256e635c6e6e794ac0d5d9.mp4?t=1726865706\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The forest is not as peaceful as it appears - ruthless creatures lurk in the underwood attracted by the scent of the flame.<br>The boy can either outrun them or manipulate his surroundings to cut them off or at least buy himself some time.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174450/extras/bf0fabf404ad777a7f39d5fa6016a7dc.poster.avif?t=1726865706\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174450/extras/bf0fabf404ad777a7f39d5fa6016a7dc.webm?t=1726865706\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174450/extras/bf0fabf404ad777a7f39d5fa6016a7dc.mp4?t=1726865706\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
